These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, video-games, gardening, camping, skydiving, reading, sudoku
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | skydiving   | camping      | reading | gardening    | video-games    | sudoku         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
House: townhouse, cottage, ranch-style, victorian, craftsman, colonial, tower
 1. the craftsman house is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the tower house##1
 3. the colonial house is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the cottage house##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the craftsman house is in the middle##1
 8. the craftsman house is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the tower house is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| House   | cottage      | ranch-style   | victorian   | craftsman      | townhouse       | tower       | colonial     |

