.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, ritmeester, dunhill, chaman, pall-mall, siglo, bongani
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 5. the bartender is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the siglo-smoker is the photographer##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | pall-mall     | dunhill  | siglo       | aristoff       | bongani  | chaman   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

