.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea, 7up, lemonade, mirinda
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | sprite | lemonade     | tea | mirinda | 7up | cola |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

