.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
7 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, monopoly, bridge, whist, mah-jongg, go
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 3. the person playing go is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person playing go##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Game   | scrabble  | go | bridge | whist | mah-jongg     | canasta | monopoly |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

