.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-15::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, june, august, february, october, january, may
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, ice-hockey, rowing, rugby, snowboarding, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6     |      7       |
| Birthday    | june | august | may     | july | february | january | october       |
| Sport   | baseball | rowing | ice-hockey | rugby     | water-polo  | climbing  | snowboarding |

